# Files in this repo that NexusMind owns.
#
# scripts/deploy_to_nexusmind.{sh,ps1} read this manifest and refuse to copy
# the listed files into the NexusMind checkout, even though they live under
# filters/common/ here. NexusMind evolves these files independently for
# production-runtime concerns (BFloat16 casts, normalization plumbing) and a
# blind sync from llm-distillery silently regresses production. See
# llm-distillery#50 and the 2026-04-19 entry in memory/gotcha-log.md for the
# incident that motivated this manifest.
#
# Format: one path per line, relative to the llm-distillery repo root. Forward
# slashes. `#` starts a comment; blank lines ignored. The deploy scripts will
# refuse to start if a listed path doesn't exist on either side (typo guard).
#
# Cross-reference: NexusMind/memory/patterns.md "Filter Sync" section is the
# upstream of this list. Update both when adding entries.

filters/common/filter_base_scorer.py
filters/common/hybrid_scorer.py
